    {
      "text": "Super Shot Soccer, known in Japan as Tecmo Sports Daiichi-dan Bakuretsu Soccer (テクモスポーツ第一弾 爆烈サッカー, Tekumosupōtsu Daiichi-dan Bakuretsu Sakkā; lit. \"Tecmo Sports Number One Shot Explosive Soccer\"), is a 2002 soccer simulation video game developed and published by Tecmo for the PlayStation. It is Tecmo's second and last soccer game released for the PlayStation, after J-League Soccer: Jikkyō Survival League.",
